section.para:
For PostgreSQL you can define a similar macro that will automatically run
the EXPLAIN command for a statemet:
explain (analyze true, verbose true, buffers true) ${current_statement}$;

For expandable macros, two special placeholders in the macro text are supported. Both placeholders are deleting when the macro text is inserted.
Parameter Description
${c}
This parameter marks the location of the cursor after the macro is expanded.
${s}
This parameter also marks the position of the cursor after expansion. Additionally the word on the right hand side of the parameter will automatically be selected.
